ab || [[Morinda]]<ref name=\"sonalika\"/> || [[Class India Limited]] || Agri Equipments\n\n|-\n| Punjab || [[Patiala]]<ref name=\"sonalika\"/> || [[John deere India Limited]] || Agri Equipments\n\n|-\n| Punjab || [[Nabha]]<ref name=\"sonalika\"/> || [[Preet Tractors Limited]] || Farm Tractors & Agri Equipments\n\n|-\n| Punjab || [[Barnala]]<ref name=\"sonalika\"/> || [[Standard Tractors Limited]] || Farm Tractors & Agri Equipments\n\n|-\n| Rajasthan || Tapukara<ref name=\"hondacarindia1\">[http://www.hondacarindia.com/about/hondaInIndia.aspx Honda in India &#124; Honda Cars India Ltd &#124; Honda Manufacturers India] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110712215724/http://www.hondacarindia.com/about/hondaInIndia.aspx |date=12 July 2011 }}</ref> || [[Honda Cars India]] || Passenger vehicles\n\n|-\n| Rajasthan || [[Alwar]]<ref name=\"ashokleyland\"/> || [[Ashok Leyland|Ashok Leyland Limited]] || Commercial vehicles\n\n|-\n| Rajasthan || [[Alwar]]<ref name=\"tafe1\"/> || [[TAFE Tractors]] || Commercial vehicles\n\n|-\n| Rajasthan || Neemrana<ref name=\"heromotocorp\">{{cite web|url=http://www.heromotocorp.com|title=Hero MotoCorp New Two Wheelers , Motorcycles, Two Wheelers in India|publisher=|accessdate=2 July 2015}}</ref> || [[Hero MotoCorp]] || Two wheelers\n\n|-\n| Rajasthan || Tapukara<ref name=\"hondaindia1\"/> || [[Honda Motorcycle and Scooter India]] || Two wheelers\n\n|-\n| Rajasthan|| [[Jaipur]] || [[Mahindra & Mahindra]] || Farm Tractors\n\n|-\n| Uttar Pradesh || [[Greater Noida]]<ref name=\"yamaha-motor-india1 Rahul\"/> || [[Yamaha Motor Company|India Yamaha Motor]] || Two wheelers\n\n|-\n| Uttar Pradesh || [[Greater Noida]]<ref name=\"hondacarindia1\"/> || [[Honda Cars India]] || Passenger vehicles\n\n|-\n\n| Uttar Pradesh || [[Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh|Greater Noida]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://agriculture1.newholland.com/apac/en-in/tools/contact-us/new-holland|title= New Holland Agriculture|publisher=|accessdate=21 March 2018}}</ref> || [[New