d vehicles\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Chennai]] || [[Isuzu]] || commercial vehicles\n|-\n|Tamil Nadu || [[Chennai]] || [[Schwing stetter]] || Commercial vehicles\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Chennai]] || [[Komatsu Limited|Komatsu]] || Dump trucks and Medium sized Excavators\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Ambattur]], [[Chennai]] || [[TI Cycles]] || Bicycles\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Maraimalai Nagar]], [[Chennai]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.india.ford.com/servlet/Satellite?c=DFYPage&cid=1178851190356&pagename=wrapper&site=FIPL|title=Virtual Plant Tour|accessdate=2 July 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111207223915/http://www.india.ford.com/servlet/Satellite?c=DFYPage&cid=1178851190356&pagename=wrapper&site=FIPL|archivedate=7 December 2011}}</ref> || [[Ford India Private Limited]] || Passenger vehicles\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Ranipet, Vellore]] || [[Bavina cars]] || Passenger vehicles\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Vellore]] || [[SAME Deutz-Fahr]] || Tractors\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Sriperumbudur]], [[Chennai]]<ref>[http://www.hyundai.com/IN/en/CompanyInfomation/AboutHMIL/Profile/HMIL/HMIL.aspx Hyundai Motor Company :: About Hyundai Motor India Ltd] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120511053350/http://www.hyundai.com/IN/en/CompanyInfomation/AboutHMIL/Profile/HMIL/HMIL.aspx |date=11 May 2012 }}</ref> || [[Hyundai Motor India Limited]] || Passenger vehicles\n\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Hosur]] || [[Caterpillar India Pvt. Limited]] || commercial vehicles\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Tiruvallur]], [[Chennai]]<ref name=\"hindmotor\"/> || [[Mitsubishi]], [[Groupe PSA]]|| Passenger vehicles\n\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [[Oragadam]], [[Chennai]]<ref>[http://www.renault.co.in/about/india.html Renault - Renault in India] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120607042658/http://www.renault.co.in/about/india.html |date=7 June 2012 }}</ref> || [[Renault India Private Limited]], [[Datsun]], [[Nissan Motor India Private Limited]] || Passenger vehicles\n|-\n| Tamil Nadu || [